1
00:01:31,410 --> 00:01:34,048
=The Glamorous Night=

2
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:39,560
(Five years ago)

3
00:01:49,058 --> 00:01:49,938
How's it? Good, right?

4
00:01:51,099 --> 00:01:51,778
Let me tell you.

5
00:01:52,138 --> 00:01:54,459
The business at nearby stores
is just average.

6
00:01:55,058 --> 00:01:56,659
Only this one is bucking the trend.

7
00:01:57,186 --> 00:01:57,938
(Zhao Mei, GST Liquor China
Promotions Department Manager)

8
00:01:57,938 --> 00:01:59,218
I designed a set meal for them.

9
00:01:59,218 --> 00:02:01,459
Over twenty sets were sold
in just half a month.

10
00:02:01,938 --> 00:02:02,659
So I was wondering

11
00:02:02,659 --> 00:02:04,619
(Dong Yue)
if you Promotions Department could help.

12
00:02:04,979 --> 00:02:05,979
(GST Liquor China, Sales Rookie)
Send some sales ladies over

13
00:02:05,979 --> 00:02:06,899
to run an event.

14
00:02:07,218 --> 00:02:08,259
No sales ladies.

15
00:02:08,259 --> 00:02:10,018
(Back then, I just switched to GST.)

16
00:02:10,779 --> 00:02:12,360
(My first time dealing with Zhao Mei.)

17
00:02:13,059 --> 00:02:14,138
(I was a sales rookie,)

18
00:02:14,698 --> 00:02:16,259
(and she was already a manager.)

19
00:02:17,738 --> 00:02:18,979
(Many people warned me)

20
00:02:19,779 --> 00:02:22,659
(to be careful
of this formidable woman.)

21
00:02:23,059 --> 00:02:23,659
Why not?

22
00:02:25,698 --> 00:02:28,099
This is not included
in my budget this year.

23
00:02:29,059 --> 00:02:30,458
Apply it three months from now.

24
00:02:32,698 --> 00:02:33,896
I'll visit stores with you.

25
00:02:35,939 --> 00:02:38,418
You're a salesman.
Why visit stores with me?

26
00:02:39,018 --> 00:02:40,578
I just want to understand the business

27
00:02:40,979 --> 00:02:43,339
from the perspective of promotion.

28
00:02:43,578 --> 00:02:44,898
It'd make my request for support

29
00:02:45,178 --> 00:02:46,939
more convincing when I apply again.

30
00:02:47,099 --> 00:02:47,979
Don't you think?

31
00:02:49,618 --> 00:02:50,219
No.

32
00:02:50,219 --> 00:02:51,059
Why not?

33
00:02:51,698 --> 00:02:52,499
Because

34
00:02:59,219 --> 00:03:00,939
I don't like taking a salesman around.

35
00:03:02,018 --> 00:03:03,659
(This woman was beautiful and proud.)

36
00:03:05,059 --> 00:03:06,018
(And I was into that.)

37
00:03:09,538 --> 00:03:15,106
(Broad and Level, Passionate,
Jump, Success Rate)

38
00:03:15,586 --> 00:03:20,514
=Episode 12=
(Overt Scheme)

39
00:03:22,858 --> 00:03:23,698
How beautiful.

40
00:03:24,499 --> 00:03:25,779
Didn't expect there is

41
00:03:26,418 --> 00:03:28,379
such a wonderful place
in Guangzhou's outskirts.

42
00:03:28,379 --> 00:03:31,298
This used to be just a reed marsh.
A tiny one.

43
00:03:32,379 --> 00:03:33,779
Later, for flood control purposes,

44
00:03:34,738 --> 00:03:36,339
they expanded this reed marsh.

45
00:03:37,458 --> 00:03:38,618
It created this lake view

46
00:03:38,738 --> 00:03:41,339
and boosted the tourism
and vacation business all around.

47
00:03:42,858 --> 00:03:43,738
Such a huge project,

48
00:03:44,738 --> 00:03:48,018
who'd do it if not for
flood control and safety?

49
00:03:49,578 --> 00:03:52,578
Many say profit
is the primary driving force.

50
00:03:53,138 --> 00:03:54,099
That's wrong.

51
00:03:55,138 --> 00:03:57,178
Fear is the primary driving force.

52
00:03:58,659 --> 00:03:59,159
Yeah.

53
00:04:00,458 --> 00:04:01,138
Peter said

54
00:04:02,138 --> 00:04:03,618
you objected to audit Zhao Mei.

55
00:04:04,698 --> 00:04:06,379
You even suggest Peter

56
00:04:07,219 --> 00:04:11,240
to have him pressure Zhao Mei
and Promotions Dept with sales targets.

57
00:04:13,359 --> 00:04:14,178
Zhao Mei

58
00:04:15,738 --> 00:04:17,192
has led Promotions for five years.

59
00:04:18,139 --> 00:04:20,498
If we audit her accounts,
I fear it might implicate...

60
00:04:20,498 --> 00:04:22,219
Don't tell me what to do.

61
00:04:22,899 --> 00:04:24,424
Think I don't know the consequences?

62
00:04:25,058 --> 00:04:27,699
I've even prepared the books,
ready for your audit.

63
00:04:29,178 --> 00:04:30,139
I know what you think.

64
00:04:31,659 --> 00:04:32,839
Auditing is a covert scheme

65
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:34,699
and pressuring with targets
is an overt one.

66
00:04:35,579 --> 00:04:38,099
You think an overt scheme
is superior to a covert one.

67
00:04:39,699 --> 00:04:40,199
Tell me.

68
00:04:40,979 --> 00:04:42,216
Since ancient times,

69
00:04:42,216 --> 00:04:44,258
why are covert schemes
used more than overt ones?

70
00:04:45,659 --> 00:04:46,779
Because others aren't smart?

71
00:04:48,298 --> 00:04:48,798
Wrong.

72
00:04:49,699 --> 00:04:51,519
Because the success rate
of overt schemes

73
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:52,858
is much lower than covert ones.

74
00:04:53,899 --> 00:04:55,058
More than that.

75
00:04:55,659 --> 00:04:58,659
Overt schemes are easy
to make you suffer.

76
00:04:58,738 --> 00:05:00,579
Suffer double losses.

77
00:05:02,378 --> 00:05:05,139
Tell me, if Zhao Mei
really hits sales targets,

78
00:05:06,139 --> 00:05:07,139
would that prove

79
00:05:08,298 --> 00:05:10,378
she's fully capable
of becoming Sales Director?

80
00:05:11,498 --> 00:05:12,659
If she really did it

81
00:05:13,459 --> 00:05:14,618
and the company promoted her,

82
00:05:15,178 --> 00:05:16,058
then I'd

83
00:05:17,058 --> 00:05:17,558
accept this.

84
00:05:21,178 --> 00:05:24,139
That's the biggest flaw
in your overt schemes.

85
00:05:24,579 --> 00:05:26,539
Just let it fail
without considering consequences.

86
00:05:27,459 --> 00:05:28,539
But think about it.

87
00:05:29,139 --> 00:05:31,298
If you dare not consider consequences,
how can you win?

88
00:05:32,219 --> 00:05:34,298
If you don't want that woman
to compete with you,

89
00:05:34,699 --> 00:05:37,899
don't give her any chance
to prove she's capable.

90
00:05:38,258 --> 00:05:39,298
Only then can you win.

91
00:05:41,579 --> 00:05:42,339
Let me tell you.

92
00:05:43,178 --> 00:05:45,298
Even if Zhao Mei
meets the sales targets,

93
00:05:46,339 --> 00:05:48,219
I still won't make her Sales Director.

94
00:05:49,418 --> 00:05:50,579
The reason is simple.

95
00:05:51,539 --> 00:05:53,298
She's not the one I choose.

96
00:05:56,659 --> 00:05:58,378
Forget it. Anyway,

97
00:05:59,139 --> 00:06:02,058
you still own an employee mindset
and don't dare go all in.

98
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:04,779
Alright, back to your work.

99
00:06:06,979 --> 00:06:07,699
Goodbye then.

100
00:06:09,418 --> 00:06:09,918
Wait!

101
00:06:13,298 --> 00:06:14,139
You and Shen Xing...

102
00:06:15,899 --> 00:06:16,899
Just a small quarrel.

103
00:06:17,618 --> 00:06:18,979
Don't take it seriously.

104
00:06:20,139 --> 00:06:21,459
I'll lecture her properly.

105
00:06:24,058 --> 00:06:26,738
Be a real man and be tolerant.

106
00:06:27,339 --> 00:06:27,979
Don't stall it.

107
00:06:29,139 --> 00:06:29,639
Got it?

108
00:06:36,418 --> 00:06:39,579
Cook the lamb,
slaughter the oxen, and celebrate.

109
00:06:40,339 --> 00:06:42,618
(Gennadiy Night)
Let's empty three hundred cups!

110
00:06:43,738 --> 00:06:46,459
Since ancient times,
the wise have always been lonely.

111
00:06:46,738 --> 00:06:49,339
Only the drinkers
leave their names behind.

112
00:06:49,418 --> 00:06:50,539
- Good!
- Good!

113
00:06:50,579 --> 00:06:51,899
- Good!
- Good!

114
00:06:52,219 --> 00:06:53,659
- Good!
- Good!

115
00:06:56,659 --> 00:06:58,858
All you heroes and warriors.

116
00:06:58,899 --> 00:07:00,219
- Come on.
- Come on.

117
00:07:00,219 --> 00:07:01,178
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

118
00:07:01,298 --> 00:07:03,858
One, two, three.

119
00:07:03,899 --> 00:07:11,659
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

120
00:07:11,659 --> 00:07:19,272
(Gennadiy Night)

121
00:07:33,659 --> 00:07:34,818
What's wrong?

122
00:07:35,099 --> 00:07:35,699
Nothing.

123
00:07:36,058 --> 00:07:37,219
Wonder what you're doing.

124
00:07:38,579 --> 00:07:40,776
Didn't you say there was an event
you need to help with?

125
00:07:42,139 --> 00:07:43,178
Where are you?

126
00:07:44,019 --> 00:07:45,818
Looks like a hotel room.

127
00:07:46,058 --> 00:07:47,459
This is my boss' room.

128
00:07:47,899 --> 00:07:49,579
There are too many clients tonight.

129
00:07:49,938 --> 00:07:51,699
She told me to stay in her room.

130
00:07:52,219 --> 00:07:55,219
Your boss? That Zhao woman, right?

131
00:07:55,738 --> 00:07:57,019
Why did she let you stay there?

132
00:07:58,699 --> 00:08:01,139
Wait, turn the camera around.

133
00:08:01,659 --> 00:08:03,058
Show me if anyone else's in there.

134
00:08:03,459 --> 00:08:04,339
What are you implying?

135
00:08:04,979 --> 00:08:06,019
I just want to check.

136
00:08:07,498 --> 00:08:09,798
Fine, check it then.

137
00:08:11,618 --> 00:08:12,118
See?

138
00:08:16,378 --> 00:08:16,938
See?

139
00:08:18,498 --> 00:08:19,099
Anyone's here?

140
00:08:21,979 --> 00:08:23,378
Here, look.

141
00:08:24,579 --> 00:08:26,378
Just an ordinary room.

142
00:08:26,378 --> 00:08:27,899
They charge over 2,000 yuan online.

143
00:08:28,938 --> 00:08:29,738
Listen.

144
00:08:30,258 --> 00:08:32,299
Don't trust everything your boss says.

145
00:08:32,699 --> 00:08:34,299
I can tell she's up to no good.

146
00:08:35,579 --> 00:08:39,059
Too many clients
and you need to stay in her room?

147
00:08:39,579 --> 00:08:42,258
I bet she just wants to make it easy
for male clients to find you.

148
00:08:42,699 --> 00:08:43,419
Get back here now.

149
00:08:43,939 --> 00:08:44,778
I also heard

150
00:08:45,258 --> 00:08:48,378
companies like this make
female staff drink with clients.

151
00:08:48,378 --> 00:08:50,472
When you're drunk,
you'd be sent to clients' rooms.

152
00:08:50,699 --> 00:08:51,738
You've cheated on me once.

153
00:08:52,179 --> 00:08:53,658
If you cheat on me again,

154
00:08:54,179 --> 00:08:56,219
I won't ever forgive you.

155
00:08:57,339 --> 00:08:58,018
Let's break up.

156
00:08:59,419 --> 00:08:59,939
What?

157
00:09:00,339 --> 00:09:02,658
If you're so scared I'll cheat on you,
then just break up.

158
00:09:10,498 --> 00:09:11,538
Annoying!

159
00:09:22,778 --> 00:09:24,018
Please sit. I'll go over there.

160
00:09:25,858 --> 00:09:26,498
Mr. Zhang.

161
00:09:27,179 --> 00:09:28,018
Long time no see.

162
00:09:30,018 --> 00:09:30,618
Here, cheers!

163
00:09:32,459 --> 00:09:32,959
Bottoms up.

164
00:09:33,959 --> 00:09:34,459
Thanks.

165
00:09:34,459 --> 00:09:35,179
Please enjoy.

166
00:09:43,819 --> 00:09:44,339
What's wrong?

167
00:09:45,299 --> 00:09:45,799
Scared?

168
00:09:47,498 --> 00:09:49,498
You've been here over a year now.

169
00:09:49,699 --> 00:09:50,498
Still scared of it?

170
00:09:51,579 --> 00:09:52,079
Scared?

171
00:09:52,459 --> 00:09:53,179
Scared of what?

172
00:09:53,459 --> 00:09:54,738
No one comes to toast me.

173
00:09:54,939 --> 00:09:56,979
I'm scared for the higher-ups here.

174
00:09:57,579 --> 00:09:59,018
What are they scared of?

175
00:09:59,498 --> 00:10:02,778
Each one here can drink
at least two bottles.

176
00:10:03,339 --> 00:10:05,138
Take Peter Du.

177
00:10:05,618 --> 00:10:07,179
He can hold his liquor for a foreigner.

178
00:10:07,339 --> 00:10:08,618
At least one bottle.

179
00:10:09,459 --> 00:10:10,939
Not to mention Shen Mo,

180
00:10:11,498 --> 00:10:12,819
he bathes in booze every day.

181
00:10:13,299 --> 00:10:15,339
He can even drink up the whole ocean.

182
00:10:15,579 --> 00:10:17,378
The two of us combined
couldn't outdrink him.

183
00:10:18,059 --> 00:10:18,979
Please support us.

184
00:10:20,219 --> 00:10:22,979
We plan to build a distillery
on Zitong Mountain.

185
00:10:23,498 --> 00:10:26,059
And integrate it
with the local tourism resources.

186
00:10:27,258 --> 00:10:29,099
Zitong Mountain is way up north.

187
00:10:29,099 --> 00:10:31,618
Yes, there's a river
called Tongbai River.

188
00:10:32,219 --> 00:10:33,579
The water in that river

189
00:10:33,579 --> 00:10:36,099
comes from melted snow on the mountains.

190
00:10:36,099 --> 00:10:37,738
It's excellent soft water.

191
00:10:37,979 --> 00:10:39,339
Perfect for making whiskey.

192
00:10:41,498 --> 00:10:41,998
Ms. Liang.

193
00:10:42,979 --> 00:10:44,059
You're truly amazing.

194
00:10:44,059 --> 00:10:45,219
You know everything.

195
00:10:45,898 --> 00:10:47,138
It's my job.

196
00:10:47,299 --> 00:10:48,658
She's a wine connoisseur.

197
00:10:48,939 --> 00:10:52,219
Others drink for work
and are reluctant to do it.

198
00:10:52,658 --> 00:10:55,618
But she genuinely loves wine.

199
00:10:56,498 --> 00:10:57,538
Mr. Shen, you get me.

200
00:10:57,538 --> 00:10:59,099
Here, let me toast you.

201
00:10:59,099 --> 00:10:59,599
Okay.

202
00:10:59,939 --> 00:11:00,618
I'll bottom up.

203
00:11:00,738 --> 00:11:01,238
Okay.

204
00:11:05,699 --> 00:11:06,339
Easy.

205
00:11:06,538 --> 00:11:07,099
Small cups.

206
00:11:07,099 --> 00:11:07,599
Tang.

207
00:11:08,219 --> 00:11:08,719
Mr. Cheng.

208
00:11:10,339 --> 00:11:10,839
Listen.

209
00:11:11,699 --> 00:11:14,099
Tonight's banquet is great in every way,

210
00:11:14,579 --> 00:11:15,579
but missing one thing.

211
00:11:16,258 --> 00:11:16,778
What is it?

212
00:11:17,179 --> 00:11:18,018
Beautiful women.

213
00:11:20,059 --> 00:11:20,979
A cake without icing.

214
00:11:21,099 --> 00:11:23,258
Not perfect anymore.

215
00:11:23,979 --> 00:11:24,658
No choice.

216
00:11:25,939 --> 00:11:27,579
You know the company's recent scandal.

217
00:11:27,778 --> 00:11:31,079
We just got off the hot seat, right?

218
00:11:31,378 --> 00:11:32,738
- Drink up.
- Come on.

219
00:11:32,738 --> 00:11:33,299
Bottoms up.

220
00:11:35,219 --> 00:11:36,018
Come on.

221
00:11:38,179 --> 00:11:38,939
I'll take a leak.

222
00:11:44,099 --> 00:11:45,319
Mr. Tang, your mouth...

223
00:11:48,419 --> 00:11:49,059
Okay.

224
00:11:49,498 --> 00:11:51,618
Tang Lide always has the most tricks.

225
00:11:52,459 --> 00:11:55,258
I've never really seen him get drunk.

226
00:11:55,898 --> 00:11:57,498
Maybe it's his age.

227
00:11:57,738 --> 00:11:58,778
He dares not drink much.

228
00:11:59,219 --> 00:12:02,059
But Mr. Dong's drinking capacity
was honed through hard practice.

229
00:12:02,498 --> 00:12:04,138
When he first joined the company,

230
00:12:04,339 --> 00:12:06,024
he could only handle
half a bottle of wine.

231
00:12:06,618 --> 00:12:10,258
Now he can handle two bottles with ease.

232
00:12:11,498 --> 00:12:13,538
He has a motto.

233
00:12:14,138 --> 00:12:16,979
"Stay drunk with a clear head,
and stay clear-headed but drunk."

234
00:12:17,378 --> 00:12:18,459
I couldn't agree more.

235
00:12:18,979 --> 00:12:19,538
Ms. Su.

236
00:12:20,419 --> 00:12:22,939
Between you and me, words aren't needed.

237
00:12:23,258 --> 00:12:25,138
Good. Toast to our cooperation.

238
00:12:28,459 --> 00:12:29,618
As for Zhao Mei,

239
00:12:30,419 --> 00:12:32,498
I haven't seen her get drunk.

240
00:12:34,378 --> 00:12:36,738
Do you think Zhao Mei
can hold her liquor?

241
00:12:37,219 --> 00:12:38,099
How would I know?

242
00:12:39,138 --> 00:12:42,339
But she's under Xu Yuntian's wing,
no one dares get her drunk.

243
00:12:42,819 --> 00:12:43,419
Look at this.

244
00:12:43,638 --> 00:12:44,138
Five.

245
00:12:44,138 --> 00:12:44,778
Look at this.

246
00:12:45,219 --> 00:12:45,738
Ten.

247
00:12:47,018 --> 00:12:48,778
Mr. Song is already drunk

248
00:12:48,778 --> 00:12:50,179
before the second round.

249
00:12:51,778 --> 00:12:53,099
Your tolerance has slipped.

250
00:12:54,018 --> 00:12:54,898
Wang Hao, come here.

251
00:12:55,018 --> 00:12:56,419
Escort Mr. Song back to his room.

252
00:12:56,419 --> 00:12:57,378
I'm not drunk.

253
00:12:57,378 --> 00:12:57,898
Come on.

254
00:12:57,898 --> 00:12:59,018
- I'm perfectly sober.
- Have some tea.

255
00:12:59,018 --> 00:13:00,258
Have some tea. Keep drinking.

256
00:13:04,299 --> 00:13:04,819
Ms. Zhao.

257
00:13:05,939 --> 00:13:06,658
Let me toast you.

258
00:13:07,018 --> 00:13:08,378
Mr. Shen, I'll toast you.

259
00:13:08,778 --> 00:13:09,378
No way.

260
00:13:09,378 --> 00:13:09,878
Bottoms up.

261
00:13:11,618 --> 00:13:13,498
Shen Mo toasts Zhao Mei.

262
00:13:16,538 --> 00:13:17,898
I remember I first met you

263
00:13:19,018 --> 00:13:20,658
at my old shop on Beishan Road.

264
00:13:21,419 --> 00:13:22,618
You came with Xu Yuntian.

265
00:13:23,018 --> 00:13:23,979
I even asked him,

266
00:13:25,538 --> 00:13:26,939
"This girl is stunning.

267
00:13:27,459 --> 00:13:28,419
Where did you get her?"

268
00:13:29,459 --> 00:13:30,459
Xu said,

269
00:13:31,059 --> 00:13:32,819
"From your shop."

270
00:13:34,099 --> 00:13:35,299
Back then,

271
00:13:35,299 --> 00:13:37,858
I was still a sales lady in your shop.

272
00:13:38,979 --> 00:13:41,738
That night
was your first time seeing me.

273
00:13:41,738 --> 00:13:43,898
But it wasn't my first time seeing you.

274
00:13:45,258 --> 00:13:46,179
Where did you see me?

275
00:13:46,979 --> 00:13:49,378
At the company's annual party
my first year.

276
00:13:49,939 --> 00:13:52,819
As a distributor representative,
you gave a speech on stage.

277
00:13:53,099 --> 00:13:55,378
I remember our chairman
personally toasted you.

278
00:13:56,299 --> 00:13:57,138
I didn't expect

279
00:13:57,258 --> 00:13:58,299
ten years passed...

280
00:13:58,299 --> 00:13:59,059
She's backing down?

281
00:13:59,059 --> 00:13:59,658
Still dashing.

282
00:13:59,939 --> 00:14:01,059
Indeed.

283
00:14:01,778 --> 00:14:03,299
She's also showing respect.

284
00:14:03,979 --> 00:14:05,258
Hard to turn him down.

285
00:14:06,898 --> 00:14:07,579
Let me do it.

286
00:14:07,898 --> 00:14:08,738
I'll do it.

287
00:14:20,179 --> 00:14:20,819
Look over there.

288
00:14:29,018 --> 00:14:30,579
She's already drunk a lot.

289
00:14:31,018 --> 00:14:33,258
Could she handle this glass of liquor?

290
00:14:36,618 --> 00:14:39,898
Liang Danning, this is not
your business. Sit down.

291
00:14:39,898 --> 00:14:41,658
Zhao Mei is my bestie.
I'll go check on her.

292
00:14:42,179 --> 00:14:43,179
- Excuse me.
- Okay.

293
00:14:48,819 --> 00:14:49,319
Mr. Shen.

294
00:14:50,699 --> 00:14:52,939
I haven't had a chance to toast you,
now's a good time.

295
00:14:53,579 --> 00:14:55,059
Ms. Zhao is a bit drunk.

296
00:14:56,339 --> 00:14:57,219
I toast you this one.

297
00:14:57,618 --> 00:14:59,579
Thank you for always looking out for me.

298
00:15:03,258 --> 00:15:04,138
Playing the hero?

299
00:15:04,459 --> 00:15:05,018
Not really.

300
00:15:06,339 --> 00:15:07,299
Good. Come on.

301
00:15:08,939 --> 00:15:09,459
Wait.

302
00:15:15,339 --> 00:15:17,099
Mr. Shen is our senior,
and we are juniors.

303
00:15:18,339 --> 00:15:19,658
For a senior to toast juniors,

304
00:15:20,138 --> 00:15:22,658
it would be disrespectful
for juniors not to drink at all.

305
00:15:23,858 --> 00:15:24,618
How about this?

306
00:15:25,099 --> 00:15:27,778
Dong Yue and I would
propose a toast to you.

307
00:15:28,059 --> 00:15:28,618
Okay.

308
00:15:30,538 --> 00:15:32,538
But this glass is too small.

309
00:15:34,339 --> 00:15:35,018
Waiter!

310
00:15:35,018 --> 00:15:35,618
Yes?

311
00:15:35,858 --> 00:15:38,258
Bring me a Burgundy glass.

312
00:15:38,579 --> 00:15:39,579
What's going on?

313
00:16:04,459 --> 00:16:05,339
I'll drink first.

314
00:16:18,979 --> 00:16:20,258
She's pushing herself.

315
00:16:57,618 --> 00:16:58,219
Good!

316
00:16:58,219 --> 00:16:59,979
- Good!
- Good!

317
00:17:48,699 --> 00:17:49,199
Good.

318
00:17:49,979 --> 00:17:50,479
Good.

319
00:17:55,738 --> 00:17:59,058
Excuse me, Miss. Perhaps
order some main dishes first?

320
00:17:59,058 --> 00:18:01,459
Our signature dishes
require longer preparation.

321
00:18:02,619 --> 00:18:04,818
No rush. My friend hasn't arrived yet.

322
00:18:05,859 --> 00:18:08,058
Bring me a latte for now.

323
00:18:08,578 --> 00:18:09,078
Okay.

324
00:18:09,219 --> 00:18:09,719
By the way,

325
00:18:11,098 --> 00:18:13,018
could you refrigerate the cake for me?

326
00:18:13,538 --> 00:18:14,179
No problem.

327
00:18:14,578 --> 00:18:15,459
Okay, thank you.

328
00:18:15,578 --> 00:18:16,578
One latte, correct?

329
00:18:16,578 --> 00:18:17,258
Just a moment.

330
00:18:44,322 --> 00:18:46,594
(Mr. Li, can I call you?
Done your work? Here's the location.)

331
00:19:07,618 --> 00:19:11,208
(Qiao Hailun)

332
00:19:16,538 --> 00:19:18,659
What's wrong? Eat up. It's delicious.

333
00:19:19,018 --> 00:19:20,179
It looks good.

334
00:19:20,179 --> 00:19:22,338
But eating carbs at this hour?

335
00:19:23,018 --> 00:19:23,699
Shut it.

336
00:19:24,699 --> 00:19:26,818
You've trained Zhao Mei
three times now, right?

337
00:19:27,058 --> 00:19:28,778
Four times. The progress is excellent.

338
00:19:29,298 --> 00:19:30,699
She's very talented.

339
00:19:30,699 --> 00:19:31,298
That's great.

340
00:19:32,098 --> 00:19:33,179
Any training records?

341
00:19:33,419 --> 00:19:33,919
Yes.

342
00:19:34,379 --> 00:19:35,498
Send them to me later.

343
00:19:36,139 --> 00:19:37,258
That might be inappropriate.

344
00:19:37,619 --> 00:19:38,859
Why is it inappropriate?

345
00:19:38,979 --> 00:19:39,939
I'm her husband.

346
00:19:39,939 --> 00:19:41,498
We hide nothing from each other.

347
00:19:42,738 --> 00:19:45,459
Besides, I only want
what's best for her.

348
00:19:46,298 --> 00:19:49,139
Zhao Mei nearly cost you
the GST project before.

349
00:19:49,538 --> 00:19:51,778
Why are you still so invested
in her promotion?

350
00:19:52,619 --> 00:19:54,498
What can I say? She's my wife.

351
00:19:55,619 --> 00:19:57,498
Spouses share responsibility.

352
00:19:57,818 --> 00:20:00,098
If she owed someone 100 million,
I'd have to repay it.

353
00:20:01,058 --> 00:20:01,578
Fine.

354
00:20:02,498 --> 00:20:05,139
I'll send you
the training records tomorrow.

355
00:20:05,818 --> 00:20:06,318
Alright.

356
00:20:08,098 --> 00:20:10,619
Zhao Mei is a good woman. Treasure her.

357
00:20:11,298 --> 00:20:12,818
Haven't I treasured her enough?

358
00:20:16,538 --> 00:20:18,298
No need to see us out. You've had a lot.

359
00:20:18,298 --> 00:20:19,258
It's okay.

360
00:20:19,258 --> 00:20:20,459
We're just heading to the spa.

361
00:20:20,459 --> 00:20:21,258
We know the way.

362
00:20:21,258 --> 00:20:22,139
Just stop here.

363
00:20:22,139 --> 00:20:22,818
You know the way?

364
00:20:22,818 --> 00:20:24,298
We do. Head back now.

365
00:20:24,298 --> 00:20:25,979
Okay. Call me.

366
00:20:25,979 --> 00:20:26,479
Bye.

367
00:20:27,058 --> 00:20:27,818
Bye.

368
00:20:29,459 --> 00:20:31,498
I just spoke with Barry.

369
00:20:31,659 --> 00:20:34,538
He explicitly stated his support
for you becoming Sales Director.

370
00:20:34,818 --> 00:20:37,018
Distributors in the southern region
also support you.

371
00:20:37,018 --> 00:20:39,979
Right now, it's one vote for Zhao Mei
and two for you.

372
00:20:40,459 --> 00:20:41,619
I thought

373
00:20:41,619 --> 00:20:43,656
Qi Youlan would follow Barry
in supporting Zhao Mei.

374
00:20:43,738 --> 00:20:45,859
(Reserve Tasting)
But she remains silent about it.

375
00:20:47,219 --> 00:20:48,498
Thank you, Peter.

376
00:20:49,058 --> 00:20:49,558
No problem.

377
00:20:50,139 --> 00:20:50,639
Good night.

378
00:21:00,098 --> 00:21:02,778
Are you available? Let's meet up if yes.

379
00:21:11,298 --> 00:21:11,798
Drunk?

380
00:21:14,298 --> 00:21:14,859
A little.

381
00:21:16,098 --> 00:21:17,979
Then why switched to such a large glass?

382
00:21:18,139 --> 00:21:19,459
Did I have a choice?

383
00:21:20,498 --> 00:21:22,379
Shen Mo was targeting me.

384
00:21:22,538 --> 00:21:24,179
If he got me drunk,

385
00:21:24,179 --> 00:21:26,538
I would be embarrassed.

386
00:21:26,818 --> 00:21:29,979
And if I let you play the hero,

387
00:21:30,139 --> 00:21:31,336
the result would be the same.

388
00:21:31,498 --> 00:21:32,818
People would think

389
00:21:33,298 --> 00:21:35,659
I couldn't even handle one distributor,

390
00:21:35,659 --> 00:21:37,018
and needed help from others.

391
00:21:37,298 --> 00:21:39,979
How could someone like me
become Sales Director?

392
00:21:42,258 --> 00:21:43,018
So,

393
00:21:44,338 --> 00:21:45,659
I had no choice.

394
00:21:46,298 --> 00:21:47,179
Let me be clear first,

395
00:21:48,219 --> 00:21:50,619
I wasn't trying to embarrass you,
but truly wanted to help.

396
00:21:52,778 --> 00:21:54,219
I know.

397
00:21:55,818 --> 00:21:56,419
So,

398
00:21:57,338 --> 00:21:58,018
thank you.

399
00:22:02,538 --> 00:22:05,459
But Shen Mo must be upset with
what you did earlier.

400
00:22:05,979 --> 00:22:07,139
You should go please him.

401
00:22:08,419 --> 00:22:08,919
No need.

402
00:22:09,659 --> 00:22:11,098
Liang Danning is handling Shen Mo.

403
00:22:12,899 --> 00:22:15,058
Do you know what's going on
between them?

404
00:22:17,619 --> 00:22:18,699
Shen Mo is ambitious.

405
00:22:19,738 --> 00:22:21,544
After his wife passed away
over a decade ago,

406
00:22:22,699 --> 00:22:23,498
he hasn't remarried,

407
00:22:23,899 --> 00:22:24,899
but he has

408
00:22:26,219 --> 00:22:26,979
many girlfriends.

409
00:22:28,258 --> 00:22:29,818
I'll thank you for Liang Danning.

410
00:22:30,058 --> 00:22:31,979
But don't worry about her.

411
00:22:32,459 --> 00:22:35,699
Liang Danning might seem carefree,

412
00:22:36,379 --> 00:22:38,498
but she has a clear head about it.

413
00:22:38,979 --> 00:22:39,778
Don't worry.

414
00:22:44,818 --> 00:22:46,298
It's so nice out here.

415
00:22:56,538 --> 00:22:57,979
You said you have something to say.

416
00:22:59,498 --> 00:23:00,219
What about now?

417
00:23:02,659 --> 00:23:03,944
I've been looking for a chance.

418
00:23:06,459 --> 00:23:08,379
But every time I want to say it, I...

419
00:23:10,619 --> 00:23:12,058
Thinking about it makes me blush.

420
00:23:13,419 --> 00:23:14,219
What for?

421
00:23:17,139 --> 00:23:18,298
Share it.

422
00:23:23,179 --> 00:23:24,498
Actually, it's nothing new.

423
00:23:24,778 --> 00:23:25,979
It's just about

424
00:23:28,459 --> 00:23:30,179
that you like me.

425
00:23:33,058 --> 00:23:34,058
I like you too.

426
00:23:35,219 --> 00:23:35,818
Really?

427
00:23:36,219 --> 00:23:36,818
Yeah.

428
00:23:38,058 --> 00:23:40,498
You're handsome and amazing,

429
00:23:41,058 --> 00:23:42,338
and you're so good to me.

430
00:23:43,219 --> 00:23:44,459
How could I resist?

431
00:23:46,219 --> 00:23:46,778
That's good.

432
00:23:48,139 --> 00:23:49,058
Just stay with me.

433
00:23:50,298 --> 00:23:51,699
But I want more than that.

434
00:23:55,379 --> 00:23:56,899
I want to be in relationship with you.

435
00:24:00,419 --> 00:24:03,699
I know this relationship
might not end well.

436
00:24:04,738 --> 00:24:06,338
But I'm not a young girl anymore.

437
00:24:07,738 --> 00:24:09,979
I enjoy the journey
and let fate lead us.

438
00:24:10,738 --> 00:24:11,659
I think it's nice.

439
00:24:13,459 --> 00:24:14,338
I have one request.

440
00:24:18,379 --> 00:24:19,058
Go ahead.

441
00:24:21,058 --> 00:24:22,139
I want you to wait for me.

442
00:24:25,699 --> 00:24:27,538
Don't laugh at me for being childish.

443
00:24:28,859 --> 00:24:30,459
Maybe I got married too early.

444
00:24:30,459 --> 00:24:31,619
I had few dating experiences.

445
00:24:32,659 --> 00:24:34,018
So I've always felt

446
00:24:34,979 --> 00:24:37,139
that a love relationship
only involves two people.

447
00:24:38,179 --> 00:24:39,578
I'm not criticizing you.

448
00:24:40,699 --> 00:24:42,338
I haven't even divorced yet.

449
00:24:42,338 --> 00:24:44,778
So I'm not qualified either.

450
00:24:46,058 --> 00:24:47,258
Do you understand what I mean?

451
00:24:50,619 --> 00:24:51,738
I want you to wait for me.

452
00:24:53,738 --> 00:24:55,939
If you still like me
after I get divorced,

453
00:24:58,058 --> 00:25:00,058
then let's be in relationship, okay?

454
00:25:26,179 --> 00:25:27,778
I heard Barry suggested

455
00:25:27,778 --> 00:25:29,098
that the new Sales Director

456
00:25:30,139 --> 00:25:31,058
be a woman.

457
00:25:34,258 --> 00:25:34,758
Yes.

458
00:25:36,098 --> 00:25:36,778
Thank him.

459
00:25:38,538 --> 00:25:40,578
You really don't hide it at all, do you?

460
00:25:44,298 --> 00:25:47,659
Do I need to hide anything from you?

461
00:25:53,139 --> 00:25:55,018
Ms. Zhao, having a private chat here?

462
00:25:55,538 --> 00:25:56,538
Chatting publicly.

463
00:25:57,058 --> 00:25:58,179
You're so nosy.

464
00:26:00,498 --> 00:26:01,578
People come and go.

465
00:26:03,738 --> 00:26:05,179
Want to talk somewhere else?

466
00:26:16,578 --> 00:26:17,419
Check please.

467
00:26:17,939 --> 00:26:18,859
Okay, just a moment.

468
00:26:29,058 --> 00:26:29,578
Hello.

469
00:26:30,859 --> 00:26:31,699
Is this Ms. Qiao?

470
00:26:32,338 --> 00:26:33,939
Delivery. I'm outside the restaurant.

471
00:26:34,738 --> 00:26:35,939
This is for you.

472
00:26:36,459 --> 00:26:36,979
Thanks.

473
00:26:36,979 --> 00:26:37,479
No problem.

474
00:26:56,699 --> 00:26:59,979
(It's not proper for us
to eat alone together in public.)

475
00:27:00,939 --> 00:27:01,659
(Happy Birthday.)

476
00:27:18,082 --> 00:27:20,744
(Residual waste)

477
00:27:23,058 --> 00:27:23,558
You okay?

478
00:27:27,298 --> 00:27:27,798
Okay.

479
00:27:35,979 --> 00:27:37,338
Should we leave the door open?

480
00:27:37,498 --> 00:27:38,179
No need.

481
00:27:38,459 --> 00:27:39,058
Close it.

482
00:27:48,179 --> 00:27:48,818
Have some more.

483
00:27:50,219 --> 00:27:51,379
More?

484
00:27:56,098 --> 00:27:58,098
Honesty requires drink.

485
00:28:25,859 --> 00:28:26,379
Yue.

486
00:28:27,258 --> 00:28:28,098
Sorry.

487
00:28:28,619 --> 00:28:29,818
I've got Xing's phone.

488
00:28:30,778 --> 00:28:31,939
She wants to sing for you.

489
00:28:33,459 --> 00:28:36,738
♪Will you still love me again♪

490
00:28:37,219 --> 00:28:40,459
♪Still hoping not to see him again♪

491
00:28:40,899 --> 00:28:46,219
♪Can I still be a clown♪

492
00:28:47,538 --> 00:28:49,419
♪Still remember in an instant♪

493
00:28:49,578 --> 00:28:50,979
♪Love was already breathtaking♪

494
00:28:51,098 --> 00:28:53,979
♪Even breathing became rapid gasps♪

495
00:29:28,298 --> 00:29:29,098
What's on your mind?

496
00:29:34,619 --> 00:29:35,498
Thinking about

497
00:29:37,098 --> 00:29:38,298
that night.

498
00:29:40,419 --> 00:29:41,939
We were like this in Shanghai too.

499
00:29:47,018 --> 00:29:49,018
You brought up that night yourself?

500
00:29:49,818 --> 00:29:50,939
Okay, I feel relieved.

501
00:30:01,058 --> 00:30:02,699
What were you worried about?

502
00:30:04,179 --> 00:30:05,018
Can't you tell?

503
00:30:06,659 --> 00:30:07,459
I'm a good person.

504
00:30:09,619 --> 00:30:10,778
You are a good person?

505
00:30:17,219 --> 00:30:18,778
You are a good person.

506
00:30:20,379 --> 00:30:23,258
Peter is pressuring me
to meet the KPIs of 50,000 cases.

507
00:30:24,538 --> 00:30:27,459
This is the first time
since GST China was established

508
00:30:27,459 --> 00:30:30,538
the Promotions Department's
got to carry sales targets.

509
00:30:36,979 --> 00:30:38,738
Aren't you the one who suggested it?

510
00:30:38,738 --> 00:30:40,098
I don't think it's a bad idea.

511
00:30:40,699 --> 00:30:41,939
Not a bad idea?

512
00:30:42,659 --> 00:30:44,018
You want to be the sales director.

513
00:30:44,058 --> 00:30:46,859
You have to make the team trust you,
so you need to achieve something.

514
00:30:48,498 --> 00:30:49,899
What about after I leave?

515
00:30:50,338 --> 00:30:52,738
The Promotions Department
still has to carry sales targets?

516
00:30:52,859 --> 00:30:55,179
When you become the director,
you can change the rules.

517
00:30:59,979 --> 00:31:02,219
50,000 cases!

518
00:31:04,419 --> 00:31:05,939
Dong Yue.

519
00:31:06,738 --> 00:31:09,058
You're killing me.

520
00:31:10,498 --> 00:31:12,338
You should be more confident.

521
00:31:13,498 --> 00:31:16,219
Now you have a chance to prove yourself.

522
00:31:16,899 --> 00:31:17,979
You can do it.

523
00:31:19,219 --> 00:31:20,699
Could you be more genuine?

524
00:31:22,219 --> 00:31:22,719
Fine.

525
00:31:24,459 --> 00:31:26,018
Actually, I just want

526
00:31:27,619 --> 00:31:28,619
to kill you.

527
00:31:36,738 --> 00:31:37,699
What did you say?

528
00:31:39,459 --> 00:31:40,419
I surrender.

529
00:31:42,419 --> 00:31:43,258
I surrender.

530
00:31:49,538 --> 00:31:50,139
Really?

531
00:31:50,538 --> 00:31:51,459
Surrender here,

532
00:31:53,058 --> 00:31:54,219
but not at the company.

533
00:32:04,459 --> 00:32:05,158
Where's Ms. Zhao?

534
00:32:05,459 --> 00:32:06,298
Not back yet.

535
00:32:06,738 --> 00:32:07,619
You are...

536
00:32:08,298 --> 00:32:11,659
She'd been drinking
with people all night

537
00:32:12,498 --> 00:32:13,699
and barely ate anything.

538
00:32:14,459 --> 00:32:16,459
I had the hotel kitchen
make her noodles.

539
00:32:16,619 --> 00:32:17,459
Is she drunk?

540
00:32:17,939 --> 00:32:19,338
The soundproofing here is terrible.

541
00:32:20,619 --> 00:32:21,859
Shouldn't have surrendered.

542
00:32:23,778 --> 00:32:26,179
Don't worry, my people won't talk.

543
00:32:28,818 --> 00:32:29,899
You really listen to her.

544
00:32:31,018 --> 00:32:32,859
Ms. Zhao is keeping you in
for your sake.

545
00:32:33,538 --> 00:32:34,979
If you go out without permission,

546
00:32:35,258 --> 00:32:36,778
you'll bear the consequences.

547
00:32:37,179 --> 00:32:39,298
Hao, do you have a thing for Ms. Zhao?

548
00:32:40,939 --> 00:32:41,939
Don't talk nonsense!

549
00:32:42,459 --> 00:32:43,219
I guessed right.

550
00:32:43,219 --> 00:32:44,098
You guessed nothing.

551
00:32:44,538 --> 00:32:45,179
Zeng Zixuan.

552
00:32:45,899 --> 00:32:47,738
You got hurt by rumors yourself.

553
00:32:48,419 --> 00:32:49,859
Don't hurt others with rumors.

554
00:33:01,578 --> 00:33:02,619
What's so funny?

555
00:33:03,018 --> 00:33:03,738
What's so funny?

556
00:33:19,338 --> 00:33:21,098
(I just received an email from your HR.)

557
00:33:21,219 --> 00:33:24,498
(They'll conduct an executive interview
with you and Dong Yue next week.)

558
00:33:25,098 --> 00:33:27,298
(Which means Barry's nomination
encountered opposition.)

559
00:33:27,538 --> 00:33:30,659
(Your higher-ups are still weighing
between you and Dong Yue.)

560
00:33:30,979 --> 00:33:32,778
(We'll discuss the details
when you get back.)

561
00:33:47,298 --> 00:33:48,818
I won't tell anyone about this.

562
00:34:00,338 --> 00:34:01,018
No more drinking.

563
00:34:03,738 --> 00:34:04,659
Go back and sleep.

564
00:34:19,819 --> 00:34:20,899
Ms. Zhao, you're back.

565
00:34:21,618 --> 00:34:23,339
Hao brought you noodles.

566
00:34:25,259 --> 00:34:25,899
I'm not eating.

567
00:34:27,979 --> 00:34:30,018
Were you planning to stay
or go home tonight?

568
00:34:30,259 --> 00:34:31,779
Hao said we're staying somewhere else.

569
00:34:31,779 --> 00:34:33,058
I'm waiting for his update.

570
00:34:34,379 --> 00:34:35,578
Then just wait in here.

571
00:34:36,979 --> 00:34:38,939
Are you in a hurry to leave?

572
00:34:38,939 --> 00:34:40,538
Yes, I have to go back to Guangzhou.

573
00:34:46,819 --> 00:34:47,319
Let me help.

574
00:34:47,899 --> 00:34:48,399
Thank you.

575
00:34:53,018 --> 00:34:54,379
(In Dong Yue's room,)

576
00:34:54,578 --> 00:34:56,739
(I experienced long-lost feelings.)

577
00:34:57,819 --> 00:34:59,819
(Excited and jumping for joy.)

578
00:35:00,459 --> 00:35:02,779
(My heart felt like being scratched)

579
00:35:03,339 --> 00:35:04,578
(by a kitten's paws.)

580
00:35:06,419 --> 00:35:08,259
(And the last time I felt this way)

581
00:35:08,618 --> 00:35:10,259
(was during my first love in college.)

582
00:35:12,178 --> 00:35:15,339
(I told myself it was just the alcohol.)

583
00:35:16,379 --> 00:35:17,779
(But I couldn't lie to myself.)

584
00:35:19,939 --> 00:35:21,178
(I had to get out of there.)

585
00:35:54,419 --> 00:35:55,018
You're home?

586
00:35:58,578 --> 00:35:59,618
This light was broken.

587
00:36:00,058 --> 00:36:01,899
It might be unsafe at night,
so I fixed it.

588
00:36:06,618 --> 00:36:07,498
Today is my birthday.

589
00:36:09,859 --> 00:36:10,658
Happy birthday!

590
00:36:26,739 --> 00:36:27,658
Take this cake.

591
00:36:29,098 --> 00:36:29,779
I didn't eat any.

592
00:36:32,618 --> 00:36:33,698
Just for the celebration.

593
00:36:35,819 --> 00:36:36,538
I'm on a diet.

594
00:36:37,979 --> 00:36:39,658
You're not fat, why are you dieting?

595
00:36:41,259 --> 00:36:41,899
For me?

596
00:36:46,018 --> 00:36:46,779
Thanks.

597
00:36:47,218 --> 00:36:48,538
I haven't eaten dinner yet.

598
00:36:55,459 --> 00:36:55,959
Ms. Qiao.

599
00:36:57,058 --> 00:36:57,558
Thank you.

600
00:36:57,939 --> 00:36:58,578
Happy birthday!

601
00:37:49,419 --> 00:37:50,299
Why are you back?

602
00:37:52,098 --> 00:37:52,819
Don't turn it on.

603
00:37:55,339 --> 00:37:57,138
Aren't you staying in Nansha?

604
00:37:58,218 --> 00:37:59,138
Why aren't you asleep?

605
00:38:01,218 --> 00:38:02,058
Are you drunk?

606
00:38:02,058 --> 00:38:02,558
Here.

607
00:38:03,498 --> 00:38:04,178
Drink the water.

608
00:38:44,299 --> 00:38:46,779
No, I'm on my period.

609
00:38:51,698 --> 00:38:52,779
That's going too far.

610
00:38:56,379 --> 00:38:57,098
I had no choice.

611
00:39:03,218 --> 00:39:04,058
It came suddenly?

612
00:39:06,618 --> 00:39:07,299
It came early.

613
00:39:08,098 --> 00:39:09,578
Fine. Bad luck.

614
00:39:11,459 --> 00:39:12,859
Why did you suddenly come back?

615
00:39:14,538 --> 00:39:15,178
Couldn't sleep.

616
00:39:20,498 --> 00:39:23,618
Barry's nomination for me was opposed
by other higher-ups?

617
00:39:24,739 --> 00:39:27,018
Yes. Two VPs opposed it,

618
00:39:27,899 --> 00:39:29,058
and one kept in silence.

619
00:39:37,819 --> 00:39:39,379
The one kept in silence was Qi Youlan?

620
00:39:39,618 --> 00:39:40,339
Exactly.

621
00:39:43,218 --> 00:39:46,299
Then her silence means opposition.

622
00:39:47,018 --> 00:39:49,339
Exactly. Go to bed now.

623
00:39:53,379 --> 00:39:56,819
Could you coach me?
The executive interview is next week.

624
00:39:57,379 --> 00:39:58,178
Now?

625
00:39:58,498 --> 00:39:59,058
Now.

626
00:40:00,618 --> 00:40:03,178
You came all this way just for this?

627
00:40:06,018 --> 00:40:07,419
Why did you tease me then?

628
00:40:10,739 --> 00:40:13,178
Just a whim. It won't happen again.

629
00:40:14,899 --> 00:40:16,419
Luring me, huh?

630
00:40:17,859 --> 00:40:19,658
Just wait. I'll make you pay for this.

631
00:40:34,842 --> 00:40:39,582
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

632
00:40:44,032 --> 00:40:45,952
♪Too much of shame♪

633
00:40:46,298 --> 00:40:49,094
♪To waste it crying♪

634
00:40:51,552 --> 00:40:53,472
♪Leave all behind you♪

635
00:40:53,472 --> 00:40:55,752
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

636
00:40:55,872 --> 00:40:58,101
♪You know how far you've gone♪

637
00:40:58,236 --> 00:41:00,512
♪In the fire you rise again♪

638
00:41:00,698 --> 00:41:03,058
♪You made it through the worst♪

639
00:41:03,196 --> 00:41:05,400
♪The best is yet to come♪

640
00:41:05,643 --> 00:41:07,783
♪The best is yet to come♪

641
00:41:10,485 --> 00:41:11,808
♪Isn't it magical♪

642
00:41:11,808 --> 00:41:13,440
♪Listen, look,
how beautiful the night is♪

643
00:41:13,472 --> 00:41:15,939
♪With countless lights on,
is someone heartbroken again♪

644
00:41:15,939 --> 00:41:18,392
♪The sound of a heart
shattering on the ground is so crisp♪

645
00:41:18,473 --> 00:41:21,121
♪Turn on a light.
A lonely heart needs comfort♪

646
00:41:21,210 --> 00:41:23,741
♪Sweat, toil, dawn, dusk♪

647
00:41:23,821 --> 00:41:26,043
♪Devaluing self-respect
just for some hot food♪

648
00:41:26,185 --> 00:41:27,266
♪But I don't want to♪

649
00:41:27,375 --> 00:41:29,641
♪Sell dignity at a price,
trampling on past vows♪

650
00:41:29,757 --> 00:41:30,822
♪Until 3 AM♪

651
00:41:30,993 --> 00:41:32,198
♪Locking dreams away in a drawer♪

652
00:41:32,352 --> 00:41:33,585
♪Just to earn some meager profit♪

653
00:41:33,676 --> 00:41:36,040
♪No matter how hard I try,
it only brings sobs♪

654
00:41:36,187 --> 00:41:40,597
♪Renewing yearly, gone with no return,
teetering, utterly bland♪

655
00:41:55,322 --> 00:41:56,758
♪Leave all behind you♪

656
00:41:56,862 --> 00:41:59,349
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

657
00:41:59,532 --> 00:42:01,661
♪You know how far you've gone♪

658
00:42:01,848 --> 00:42:04,188
♪In the fire you rise again♪

659
00:42:04,256 --> 00:42:06,522
♪You made it through the worst♪

660
00:42:06,882 --> 00:42:08,960
♪The best is yet to come♪

661
00:42:09,209 --> 00:42:11,379
♪The best is yet to come♪

662
00:42:14,080 --> 00:42:15,232
♪Isn't it magical♪

663
00:42:15,232 --> 00:42:18,878
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

664
00:42:18,912 --> 00:42:20,768
♪And I see them sparkling♪

665
00:42:20,992 --> 00:42:23,123
♪Nobody knows♪

666
00:42:23,744 --> 00:42:25,654
♪What tomorrow brings♪

667
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:28,243
♪You made it through the worst♪

668
00:42:28,430 --> 00:42:30,638
♪The best is yet to come♪

669
00:42:30,925 --> 00:42:33,074
♪The best is yet to come♪

670
00:42:33,370 --> 00:42:34,784
♪Isn't it magical♪

671
00:42:34,784 --> 00:42:36,996
♪Feeling uneasy,
yet no one's chasing me♪

672
00:42:37,070 --> 00:42:39,424
♪Retreating step by step,
everything turning to ash♪

673
00:42:39,424 --> 00:42:40,512
♪I'm silent, I'm roaring♪

674
00:42:40,512 --> 00:42:43,963
♪This helplessness
keeps pushing me towards the cliff♪

675
00:42:44,416 --> 00:42:46,690
♪Trembling legs
carry away a shattered soul♪

676
00:42:47,104 --> 00:42:47,968
♪Who wants to be just a passerby♪

677
00:42:47,968 --> 00:42:49,488
♪Isn't it magical♪
